    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    App
    Entry point for the BTO Management System application.
    Applicant
    Represents an Applicant user in the BTO Management System.
    ApplicantDAO
    DAO (Data Access Object) class responsible for managing data related to Applicants.
    ApplicantEnquiryView
    Represents the applicant view for managing enquiries.
    ApplicantManageApplicationView
    Provides the view layer for applicants to manage their BTO applications.
    ApplicantProjectStatus
    Represents the application status of an applicant for a specific BTO project.
    ApplicantView
    The main user interface for applicants in the BTO Management System.
    ApplicantViewApplyProjectView
    View class that handles user interaction when an applicant is applying for a BTO project.
    ApplicantViewProjectsView
    View class responsible for displaying project listings and eligibility messages to applicants in the BTO Management System.
    ApplicationController
    Controller class responsible for handling Applicant applications
    ApplicationProjectStatusDAO
    DAO class that manages application records for applicants applying to BTO projects.
    ApplicationStatus
    Enumeration representing the various statuses an application can have in the BTO Management System.
    ApplicationStatusController
     
    AuthController
    Controller class responsible for handling user authentication logic.
    AuthenticatorService
    Provides authentication services for users attempting to log in to the BTO Management System.
    BookingController
    Controller class responsible for handling the booking of flats for applicants who have been successfully approved for a BTO project.
    Enquiry
    Represents an enquiry submitted by an applicant for a BTO project.
    EnquiryController
    Controller class that handles all enquiry-related operations within the BTO Management System.
    EnquiryDAO
    Data Access Object (DAO) for managing Enquiry objects.
    EnquiryView
     
    FlatType
    Enumeration representing the types of flats available in the BTO Management System.
    HDBManager
    Represents an HDB Manager in the BTO Management System.
    HDBManagerApproveBTOApplicationView
    View class for HDB Managers to approve BTO applications.
    HDBManagerApproveOfficerView
    View class used by HDB Managers to handle officer registration requests.
    HDBManagerCreateProjectView
    View class that handles the user interface for HDB Managers to create a new BTO project.
    HDBManagerDAO
    DAO (Data Access Object) class responsible for managing data related to HDB Managers.
    HDBManagerDeleteProjectView
    View class responsible for interacting with HDB Managers during the project deletion process.
    HDBManagerEditProjectView
    View class used by HDB Managers to edit existing project details.
    HDBManagerEnquiryView
    View class for HDB Managers to manage enquiries.
    HDBManagerView
    View class for the HDB Manager dashboard interface.
    HDBManagerViewProjectsView
    View class responsible for displaying project-related information and filtering options for the HDB Manager.
    HDBManagerWithdrawalRequestView
    View class for HDB Managers to manage withdrawal requests from applicants.
    HDBOfficer
    Represents an HDB Officer in the BTO Management System.
    HDBOfficerAssignedProjectView
    View class for HDB Officers to manage operations related to their assigned project.
    HDBOfficerDAO
    DAO (Data Access Object) class responsible for managing data related to HDB Officers.
    HDBOfficerEnquiryView
    View class that allows HDB Officers to manage enquiries within the BTO management system.
    HDBOfficerProjectRegistrationView
    View class for handling officer registration-related interactions within the BTO Management System.
    HDBOfficerView
    The HDBOfficerView class represents the main dashboard and interface for an HDB Officer within the BTO Management System.
    LoginPromptView
    The LoginPromptView class handles user interaction for the login screen of the BTO Management System.
    MenuViewController
    Controller class responsible for directing users to their respective main menu views based on their role (Applicant, HDB Officer, or HDB Manager).
    OfficerRegistrationController
    Controller class responsible for handling officer registration requests to projects.
    OfficerRegistrationRequest
    Represents a registration request made by an HDB Officer to be assigned to a BTO project.
    OfficerRegistrationRequestDAO
    DAO (Data Access Object) class for managing officer registration requests.
    PasswordController
    Controller class responsible for handling user password changes in the system.
    Project
    Represents a Build-To-Order (BTO) project within the HDB system.
    ProjectListController
    Controller class responsible for handling operations related to BTO project management.
    ProjectListDAO
    DAO (Data Access Object) for managing BTO Project data.
    Receipt
    Represents a receipt issued to an applicant after a successful BTO flat booking.
    ReceiptController
    Controller class responsible for managing receipt-related operations, including generation and viewing of booking receipts based on filters.
    ReceiptsDAO
    DAO (Data Access Object) class for managing receipt records related to successful BTO applications.
    ReceiptsView
    The ReceiptsView class handles the presentation layer for viewing and filtering receipt records in the BTO Management System.
    SessionManagerService
    Handles the creation and management of user sessions in the BTO Management System.
    User
    Represents a generic user in the BTO Management System.
    WithdrawalRequest
    Represents a request made by an applicant to withdraw from a BTO project application.
    WithdrawalRequestController
    Controller class responsible for handling applicant withdrawal requests.
    WithdrawalRequestDAO
    DAO (Data Access Object) class responsible for managing BTO withdrawal requests.
